{"article_id":"Zt6RO6Syc6aqs5LL","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"US President Donald Trump is set to argue","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"that an immigration `` crisis '' requires his long-promised wall along the Mexican border .","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"Mr Trump will make his case in his first speech from the Oval Office at 21:00EST","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"( 0200 GMT Wednesday ) ,","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"ahead of a trip to the border on Thursday .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"A partial government shutdown has been in effect for 17 days","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"after lawmakers failed to break a budget impasse .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"The president is insisting","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"that $ 5bn","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"( £4bn )","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"be included for the border wall .","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"White House press secretary Sarah Huckabee Sanders said in a tweet","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"that Mr Trump would use his visit to the border on Thursday","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"to `` meet with those on the front lines of the national security and humanitarian crisis '' .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"Ahead of the speech on Tuesday , Vice-President Mike Pence said","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"Mr Trump 's decision","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"to address the nation","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"`` comes from this president 's deep desire","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"to do his job","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"to protect the American people '' .","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"Donald Trump says","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"there is a growing crisis along the US-Mexico border","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"that demands immediate and drastic action .","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"The challenge for Mr Trump is that he has been calling for a wall","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"- a bigger , longer one -","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"since he announced his presidential bid in 2015 .","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"That has made it hard for his opponents to believe","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"there is a new situation","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"that requires the same solution , except smaller and shorter .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"What 's more , administration officials have been vague","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"- perhaps intentionally -","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"on the numbers","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"supporting their claims .","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"They say","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"4,000 `` terrorists '' have been caught entering the US ,","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"but it turns out most stops happen at airports .","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"There have been only a handful","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"apprehended at the Mexican border","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"( fewer than at the border with Canada ) .","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"The White House has recently painted this as a humanitarian problem","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"- and Central American families are , in fact , fleeing poverty and violence .","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"But can he make the case","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"that a wall is the humanitarian answer ,","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"and not just a way","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"of making refugee suffering less visible to Americans ?","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"The president must convince a sceptical public","depth":3},{"id":46,"text":"that his wall is worth the pain","depth":4},{"id":47,"text":"the shutdown is causing government workers and the nation at large .","depth":4},{"id":48,"text":"The decision by the major US TV networks","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"to set aside at least eight minutes of airtime for the speech","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"has sparked controversy","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"and fuelled debate on social media .","depth":5},{"id":52,"text":"Critics pointed out","depth":5},{"id":53,"text":"that the networks aired President George W Bush 's prime-time address on immigration in 2006 ,","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"but did not air one by President Barack Obama in 2014 .","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"Democratic House Speaker Nancy Pelosi and Senate Minority Leader Chuck Schumer announced on Tuesday","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"that they would deliver a joint rebuttal from the halls of Congress","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"after Mr Trump has spoken .","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"Some reporters have called on the White House to provide the text of his remarks in advance","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"to be fact-checked .","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"On Monday , living former US presidents disputed Mr Trump 's claim","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"that some of them had privately told him","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"they regretted not building a border wall during their administrations .","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"`` I have not discussed the border wall with President Trump ,","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"and do not support him on the issue , ''","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"former President Jimmy Carter said in a statement","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"issued by the Carter Center on Monday .","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"A spokesman for George W Bush said","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"he had never discussed the border wall with Mr Trump .","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"A representative for Bill Clinton denied it","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"and said","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"that the two men had not spoken","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"since Mr Trump took office ,","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"according to CBS .","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"Mr Obama has not explicitly denied Mr Trump 's claim ,","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"but has extensively campaigned against the president on the issue .","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"In Mr Pence 's interview with NBC on Tuesday , he sought to clarify the president 's original claim ,","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"`` that was his impression from previous administrations , previous presidents '' .","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"`` I know","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"I 've seen clips of previous presidents","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"talking about the importance of border security , the importance","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"of addressing the issue of illegal immigration , ''","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"he added .","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"The White House has been under fire amid a partial government shutdown ,","depth":5},{"id":85,"text":"which began on 22 December","depth":6},{"id":86,"text":"and affects a quarter of the government .","depth":6},{"id":87,"text":"Some 800,000 federal employees have been temporarily laid off","depth":6},{"id":88,"text":"- or are working","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"without pay .","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"Nine departments have been affected ,","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"including Homeland Security , Justice , Housing , Agriculture , Commerce , Interior and the Treasury .","depth":6},{"id":92,"text":"US media are reporting","depth":6},{"id":93,"text":"that Mr Trump will not declare a national emergency on Tuesday evening , in a bid","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"to launch construction of a wall","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"by circumventing Congress .","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"US law allows the president to direct military construction projects during war or national emergency ,","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"but that money would have to come from defence department funds","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"allocated by Congress for other purposes ,","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"the BBC 's Anthony Zurcher says .","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"Such a move would prompt members of Congress","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"who are tasked with allocating tax money","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"- including some Republicans -","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"to push back ,","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"he says .","depth":7},{"id":105,"text":"Curbing illegal immigration was one of the main campaign promises","depth":6},{"id":106,"text":"Mr Trump made","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"when he ran for president in 2016 .","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"During the campaign for the mid-term elections in November 2018 , he repeatedly warned of a `` caravan '' of Central American migrants","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"making its way towards the US-Mexico border .","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"In a reaction","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"that many saw as a political ploy during a campaign season ,","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"he deployed 5,800 US troops to the border","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"due to what he described as an `` invasion '' .","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"Last month , Mr Trump suggested","depth":7},{"id":115,"text":"that the US military could be used","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"to build the wall .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":233,"left":164,"right":232,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":164,"left":161,"right":163,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":161,"left":136,"right":160,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":136,"left":121,"right":135,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":118,"right":120,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":118,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":120,"left":119,"right":4,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":119,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":135,"left":126,"right":134,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":126,"left":122,"right":125,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":122,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":7,"right":124,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":124,"left":123,"right":10,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":123,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":134,"left":128,"right":133,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":128,"left":11,"right":127,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"